data.description: Welcome to this townhome in Rolling Crest! Your future home offers 3 Bedrooms and 2.5 Bathrooms. The main level has a Living Room/Dining Room combo with Walnut Laminated Flooring, and a Kitchen. The eat in- Kitchen features new granite-slab countertops, a bay window, and a pass-through window to the dining area—great for entertaining guests! Open the french doors off the living room and enjoy your favorite BBQ on the deck overlooking the fenced yard. Easy stair access from the deck to the yard! Upstairs, you'll find 3 Bedrooms, including the Primary, which has a private dressing/vanity area with a sink and a walk-in closet. The walnut floors continue downstairs, where you’ll find a walkout basement with track lighting, a Family/Rec Room and full Bath. From the basement, set up a few chairs on the covered patio, and unwind! The fenced yard backs to a beautiful wooded area with mature trees, offering privacy and views! Call now to schedule your showing!
